w"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/vtuber-gundo-mirei-criticized-for-problematic-comments-during-wbc-live-streaming/">VTuber Gundo Mirei WBC直播中有问题言论遭多方批评 各家媒体纷纷报道</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“VTuber Gunmichi Mirei在WBC直播时的言论被批，各家媒体纷纷报道”——P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/vtuber-gundo-mirei-criticized-for-problematic-comments-during-wbc-live-streaming/embed/#?secret=3Dd32R59DC#?secret=L4aSUMWpbw" data-secret="L4aSUMWpbw" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><p></p><p>此后，ANYCOLOR于3月23日宣布Gundo先生将被禁止活动。该处置持续至 5 月 31 日。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="bFpBTj1XKU"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/anycolor-suspends-nijisanji-vtuber-gundo-mirei-due-to-problematic-comments-about-world-baseball-classic/">ANYCOLOR Inc. Nijisanji VTuber Mirei Gundo 被暂停活动，提及他过去的行为也不合适</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“ANYCOLOR Inc. Nijisanji VTuber Mirei Gundo 因活动被停职并提到他过去的行为不当” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/anycolor-suspends-nijisanji-vtuber-gundo-mirei-due-to-problematic-comments-about-world-baseball-classic/embed/#?secret=yt2koDgM6I#?secret=bFpBTj1XKU" data-secret="bFpBTj1XKU" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><p></p><div class="dxsyj64773d27beb7f" ><script async src="https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-3186024119059876"
